==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|everichon|lang=enm}}, equivalent to {{compound|every|one|lang=en}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{audio|en-us-everyone.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Pronoun===
{{en-pron}}

